{ 'html':'<article>         <div class="inCon">         <h1>World Wu Tan Kuoshu Federation (WWKF)</h1><span class="path"><a href="index.php">Home</a> > <b>World Wu Tan Kuoshu Federation</b></span>               <h2>Origin</h2><a name="organization-overview" id="organization-overview"></a>         <p>This federation is an international platform formed by disciples of Grandmaster Liu Yunqiao—without presidents or hierarchy, united through martial arts and shared principles.<br>Grandmaster Liu-s Baji, Bagua, and Praying Mantis styles emphasize both skill and virtue—the way is embodied in the fist, passed down through generations.</p>         <h3>Mission</h3>         <ol>             <li>Preserve authentic lineage</li>             <li>Unify skill and virtue</li>             <li>Global community of fellow disciples</li>         </ol>         <p></p>         <p>A global, non-profit platform formed by disciples of Grandmaster Liu Yunqiao—without titles or ranks, united in martial spirit and shared path. <br>Grandmaster Liu-s Bajiquan, Baguazhang, and Tanglangquan emphasize both skill and virtue—his teachings live on through action and heart.</p>                 <h3>Mission</h3>         <ol>             <li>Preserve authentic lineage</li>             <li>Cultivate skill and virtue</li>             <li>Unite disciples worldwide</li>         </ol>         <p></p>                 <h2>Logo</h2><a name="wwkf-logo" id="wwkf-logo"></a>         <p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wutang.tw/images/WWKF-LOGO.png" class="wwkf-logo"></p>                 </div>         <div class="clear"></div>     </article> '}